title: Overcome Shy Bladder
description:
Shy Bladder also known as Pee-Shy, Paruresis, Bashful Bladder is a condition in which a person finds it difficult to urinate in public toilets.
If you have this problem just listen to this audio tape in trance state or during early morning (closer to wake up time) for 2-3 days (vary from person to person)

Visit http://prince213.blogspot.com/ for more...
